data.description: You don't want to miss out on this beautifully maintained home in the sought after Tuscany subdivision. This home has had only one owner and has been kept in pristine condition. The downstairs not only boasts an open concept kitchen and living area, but a bedroom with a full bath. Venture upstairs and you will find a spacious master bedroom with a beautiful adjoining bathroom which includes a relaxing garden tub and massive master closet. On the second level you will also find two more bedrooms and another full bath. As if that wasn't enough, the second floor also has a large loft area perfect for an office space or bonus room. Lastly, this property has a beautiful back yard and a two car garage that is temperature controlled. If you're looking for a space to make your own, look no more. Schedule your showing today!
